{"tid":2203578,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"台灣不是中國的嗎？ - 高慧然","createTime":"2020-09-15T12:16:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T16:44:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0b9e9bf7c1e6611d880ed6478aab860fe30443a6","tid":2203578,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T12:16:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200915/3JPBYKFRW5CG3DKTBLR4P6M3MI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200915%2F3JPBYKFRW5CG3DKTBLR4P6M3MI%2F&d=ulKCtXgG4rwmRR8qyGKIuQVsaiM9baN%2FEtUhsAXiQ7E%3D&h=41c9ad1a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200915%2F3JPBYKFRW5CG3DKTBLR4P6M3MI%2F&h=06ca1360\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200915/3JPBYKFRW5CG3DKTBLR4P6M3MI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n台灣不是中國的嗎？ - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/KwAX9_TLC7DA4VEv8HUmZBNEP0Q=/786x449/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3YHMDD5T4JDX7BE5KWFN63YJCM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FKwAX9_TLC7DA4VEv8HUmZBNEP0Q%3D%2F786x449%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3YHMDD5T4JDX7BE5KWFN63YJCM.png&h=1f5f41ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n12個香港人從香港坐船去台灣，結果被中國水警捕捉，迄今尚未能與外界接觸，甚至連家屬及其家屬委派的律師都不能見到他們。為甚麼？據悉罪行嚴重。深圳公安鹽田分局表示他們觸犯的是「偷越國家邊境罪」，而中國外交部發言人華大媽則在Twitter指出這12個香港人是「企圖將香港分裂出中國者」（elements attempting to separate Hong Kong from China）。<br />\n<br />\n這就怪了，根據中國官方說法，香港固然是屬於中國的，台灣亦是中國不可分割的一部分，名為「中國台灣省」。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n如果12個香港人從廣東省香港巿去中國台灣省是犯下彌天大罪，那麼，以後廣東省深圳巿民去中國四川省，又或者北京人去上海等，犯下的同樣是「偷越國家邊境罪」，同樣是「將深圳分裂出中國」，或者「將北京分裂出中國」&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n不過到目前為止，有限的資訊由中方發放，12名被捕者生不見人、死不見屍，他們究竟在哪個水域被捕，是中國的香港水域、中國水域、中國的台灣省水域，抑或公海？其實無人得知，所以他們如何坐在一隻艇上就很厲害地把香港從中國分裂出去，變成一個獨立的地方，世人不得而知而又充滿遐想。不如讓他們出來示範一次？"},{"pid":"9c71ad13220275849063561b9af84ee322de9de3","tid":2203578,"uid":10274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T12:36:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ead10c8caffeed4f9b594c33ae0f60076ee4a23","tid":2203578,"uid":356542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T16:44:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}